column2: Nevertheless,  in  the written submission filed  in this  Court by the  learned
Counsel for the Accused - Petitioner, it was contended that the  fine  imposed
by  the  learned  High  Court  Judge  has  already  been  paid  in  respect  of the
imprisonment that had not been suspended by the learned High Court Judge.

column1: By  this  Petition  the  Accused  - Petitioner,  has  sought  to  suspend  the  30

column2: months rigorous imprisonment imposed by the learned High Court Judge.
